\newlabel{fig:crystallization}{{8}{8}{Geometric structure at the crystallization point. Left: 3D PCA decomposition at L24 showing temporal encoding structure. Right: MLP output trajectories across layers showing the bifurcation at L24 where continuous temporal gradients separate into stable decision bands}{figure.caption.20}{}}
