\newlabel{fig:direction}{{9}{9}{Direction dynamics through the circuit. Left: Layer-to-layer cosine similarity showing stability with dips at integration points. Right: Alignment to the logit-difference direction---near-zero through processing layers until late rotation at L34--L35}{figure.caption.21}{}}
